https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=25542	21840
Google将在年底<a href="__SLASHLINK__" sect="it" sid="11/08/10/0737216" sn="article" tid="26">关闭</a>教育工具Android App Inventor，让外界颇感失望。但事态发展旋即又峰回路转，<a href="http://appinventorblog.com/2011/08/16/best-app-inventor-news-ever-mit-launches-new-center-for-mobile-learning/">MIT接过了Google的烫手山芋</a>。<i>
